Prerequisites
Ensure the following are installed on your server:

Docker (20.10+)
Docker Compose (2.0+)
Git

Quick Deployment
1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/virtuositydev/casino-webscraper.git
cd casino-webscraper

2. Configure Environment (Optional)
Edit docker-compose.yml if you want to change settings

nano docker-compose.yml

# Key settings you might want to adjust:
# - TZ=Asia/Manila (timezone)
# - MAX_PAGES_PER_CASINO=None (scraping limit)
# - Cron schedule: 0 8 * * * (daily at 8 AM)

3. Build and Start

docker-compose build

# Start the containers
docker-compose up -d

# Verify containers are running
docker-compose ps

4. Verify Installation

# Check logs
docker-compose logs -f casino-scraper

# Run scraper manually (first test)
docker-compose exec casino-scraper python casino_scraper.py

# Check output
ls -lah output/

# Verify cron job is set up
docker-compose exec casino-scraper crontab -l

Daily Operation
The scraper runs automatically every day at 8:00 AM via cron.

Manual Trigger
docker-compose exec casino-scraper python casino_scraper.py

View Logs
docker-compose logs -f casino-scraper

# View specific log file
ls -lah logs/
tail -f logs/scraper_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.log

Access Data
# View scraped data
ls -lah output/

# List all promo folders
ls -lah output/promo_*/

# View jackpots
cat output/promo_TIMESTAMP/_jackpots.json

# View index
cat output/promo_TIMESTAMP/_index.json

Maintenance
Stop/Start/Restart
# Stop
docker-compose stop

# Start
docker-compose start

# Restart
docker-compose restart

# Stop and remove
docker-compose down

Update Script
# Pull latest changes
git pull origin main

# Restart containers
docker-compose restart casino-scraper

